&ldquo;If you can&rsquo;t understand it without an explanation, you can&rsquo;t understand it with an explanation.&quot;
- 1Q84
 What most surprised me about 1Q84 is that I actually liked reading it! I have read enough Murakami that as I was reading the book I knew that he was not going to explain anything and yet I did not feel frustrated. I have developed a taste for his writing.
